NOTE
====

This is not the original work. It was modified by Matteo Franchin,
to highlight Box sources and make automatic webpages containing correctly
highlighted Box example programs. See the note at the end for more info
about the copyright and about the original author.

Syntax-Highlight-Engine-Kate version 0.01
=========================================


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
   
DEMOS

Following demos have been provided. hlhtml.pl and hlansi.pl. After
the make command you may want to try something like:

   cat bin/hlhtml.pl | perl -Mblib bin/hlansi.pl Perl

or

   cat bin/hlhtml.pl | perl -Mblib bin/hlhtml.pl Perl > tst.html
   
just to get an overview of what this module actually does.

